{"tid":808454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 玩自動波車係唔係戇鳩","createTime":"2018-09-06T10:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T14:21:19.000Z","uid":104848,"like":2,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed3f18e1f30331bba415eb42cb4a0fa2b7866b5","tid":808454,"uid":104848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"你話自動波車用黎搵食/車人出入/要舒適嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你可以返回上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係如果話攞嚟玩嘅,就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個波箱乜都幫你做晒決定, 究竟你係控制緊架車定架車控制緊你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半自動+/-仲搞笑,兩頭唔到岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你拍返入個D波,你就乜都唔係。<br />\n<br />\nDual Clutch Gear Box轉波係快,係開心既。但係一壞波箱你就真係企喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識呢D車揸嘅人就大修波箱無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSequential連 Clutch嘅不計算在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩車嘅應該要識安全地踭趾拖波補油,冼拿上身咁, 咁先可以話自己控制到部車<br />\n<br />\n咁年青人，究竟有咩動力，驅使你買自動波車嚟玩呀？係愛呀？定係責任？"},{"pid":"178fe7be6d734977394d1a146df41a54980dbe6d","tid":808454,"uid":100760,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"為咗車出車入同舒適"},{"pid":"e28351cf3d69ef7228d8c2282904339abec66576","tid":808454,"uid":78632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:46:31.000Z","msg":"依家棍波車都有自動補油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbd722d093be156c122afae10955469da6bf23a","tid":808454,"uid":121005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s